-- Lions Gate Poison Pill Aimed at Detering Ichan Voided by Canada Regulator
-- Joe Schneider
-- 2010-04-27T22:07:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-27/lions-gate-poison-pill-aimed-at-detering-ichan-voided-by-canada-regulator.html

          
          
             Lions Gate Entertainment Corp.’s
poison pill, intended to deter investor Carl Icahn from pursuing
a takeover of the studio by making it more expensive, was
annulled by Canadian regulators who said shareholders deserved
the opportunity to respond to Icahn’s $7 a share offer.  
